"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/79345","Department for Energy and Climate Change","false","2014-09-02","<p>I refer the hon. Member to the answer I gave him on 1 September 2014, <em>Official Report</em>, Column 113-114W.</p><p> </p>","Hastings and Rye","Amber Rudd",,"2014-09-02T15:26:59.6041824Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/79345/answer","Biography information for Amber Rudd","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/79345/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/79345/answer",,,,,"63","Energy and Climate Change","Energy and Climate Change","2014-07-22","Solar Power: Renewables Obligation","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Energy and Climate Change, what recent discussions he has had on the maintenance of the current 20-year duration support level for accredited solar PV plants and the Renewables Obligation order; what his policy is on this matter; and if he will make a statement.","false","Biography information for Grahame Morris","Easington","Grahame M. Morris","206960"
